##  Why This Matters

As GRC leaders, itâ€™s not enough to say â€œsecure everything.â€  
**Resources are finite â€” so prioritization is key.**

By documenting the system as **Moderate**, Iâ€™m guiding:

 The **engineering team** â€” so they select controls proportional to risk.  
 The **executive team** â€” so they understand the business impact of outages or breaches.  
 The **audit/compliance function** â€” so they see how our categorization maps to required controls (HIPAA, NIST 800-53, etc.).

